{3: 'Aside from the residual hums within the central purification filter chamber, you do not feel any differences.'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'The Corrupted are retreating... Did it work, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Yep. The filter is online.', 3: '141'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Now then, only one thing left to do...'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Now then, only one thing left to do...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'The mainframe of the control center is here.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "If the engies are renovating this place, this kid'll have to be shut off first.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: 'Cosmos Industries MSC-43B. In service for ■■■■■ days.'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: 'Log: ■■/■■/■■■■. Registered large quantities of unidentified hostile entities. Modified functions to protect evacuating humans.'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: 'Log: ■■/■■/■■■■. Partial withdrawal of unidentified hostile entities due to high-frequency signal broadcast from coordinates: ■■■.'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: 'Log: ■■/■■/■■■■. To sustain current functionality, Emergency Protocol 331A has been executed. All external ports disconnected.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'What a champ... Even popping 331A...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: 'Control Logs: This terminal has been running ■■■■■ days past standard operation limits.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "The logs are overflowin' too... Commandant, shut it down already.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Even machines need rest. And this boyo deserves one more than any other.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Turn off the terminal', 3: '160'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: 'System shutdown... confirmed.'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: 'Cosmos Industries... Excellence and reliability in design...'}
{2: 'Control Terminal', 3: '...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Man, they need to pay you more for this. "Reliability in design", huh... Guess that\'s not just sales talk.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "That's one hell of an overtime... Sleep tight, sweet prince.", 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'Hello? Do you copy? According to the reports from the nearby task force squads, most of the Corrupted around the filter chamber should be exterminated.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'Engineering and Support Forces are en route.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "Good work, everyone. Take five. We'll send you the intel for the next area later.", 4: '2'}
